OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1784908087
OL,3,CFather jailed for life after murdering
OL,4,Cnewborn baby by shaking him
OL,6,FBartlett and his then-partner, Evelyn
OL,7,FBallentyne, Atticus's mother, had gone
OL,8,Fto a pub and comedy club that evening.
OL,10,FMs Ballentyne's mother Rachel Donovan
OL,11,Fand her husband went to the family's
OL,12,Fhome on Darcis Row, Chard, to care for
OL,13,FAtticus.
OL,15,FOver the evening, Bartlett drank 8.5
OL,16,Fpints of lager before returning home
OL,17,Fwith Ms Ballentyne.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1784908087
OL,3,CFather jailed for life after murdering
OL,4,Cnewborn baby by shaking him
OL,6,FMr Row told the court: "Evelyn
OL,7,FBallentyne went upstairs for a few
OL,8,Fminutes, leaving Atticus in the
OL,9,Fdefendant's sole care.
OL,11,F"When she returned, Atticus was lying
OL,12,Fface down across the defendant's lap.
OL,14,F"She said 'he's dead, he's not
OL,15,Fbreathing'. She noted that the
OL,16,Fdefendant appeared to be asleep or at
OL,17,Fleast his eyes were closed.
OL,19,F"The defendant flipped Atticus over.
OL,20,FAtticus released two gasps and
OL,21,Fappeared to be floppy and lifeless."
OL,26,@nD@XOUsD@AOUvD@AOU{D@AOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1784908087
OL,3,CFather jailed for life after murdering
OL,4,Cnewborn baby by shaking him
OL,6,FEmergency services attended the
OL,7,Fproperty and Atticus was taken to
OL,8,FMusgrove Park Hospital before being
OL,9,Ftransferred to Bristol Royal Hospital
OL,10,Ffor Children.
OL,12,FHis brain damage was so severe he did
OL,13,Fnot regain consciousness or breathe
OL,14,Ffor himself.
OL,16,FAtticus died just before midnight on
OL,17,F23 July 2022.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1784908087
OL,3,CFather jailed for life after murdering
OL,4,Cnewborn baby by shaking him
OL,6,FExperts said the injuries suffered by
OL,7,FAtticus were associated with "vigorous
OL,8,Fshaking", with his rib fractures
OL,9,Fcaused by "gripping and squeezing"
OL,10,Fduring that attack, Mr Row told the
OL,11,Fcourt.
OL,13,FIn a victim personal statement, Ms
OL,14,FBallentyne described how she had been
OL,15,Fleft with "severe anxiety" following
OL,16,FAtticus's death.
OL,18,F"I will never know what kind of person
OL,19,FAtticus would have become," she said.
OL,26,@oD@^OUpD@HO]qD@KOUqD@bO]wD@KOUwD@ZO]zD@
OL,26,AAOU{D@[O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1784908087
OL,3,CFather jailed for life after murdering
OL,4,Cnewborn baby by shaking him
OL,6,F"I will never see him hit milestones.
OL,7,FI will never see him go to school. I
OL,8,Fwill never see him grow up and have a
OL,9,Ffamily of his own."
OL,11,FShe continued: "Who plans their baby's
OL,12,Ffuneral? Who goes to the chapel of
OL,13,Frest?
OL,15,F"I had to wait 11 hours and 18 minutes
OL,16,Ffor Atticus to die. It was horrendous.
OL,17,FI was scared to go out, I was scared
OL,18,Fto stay in.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@SO]sD@POUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1784908087
OL,3,CFather jailed for life after murdering
OL,4,Cnewborn baby by shaking him
OL,6,F"I don't enjoy any moments because I
OL,7,Fhave a dead son. It is mentally and
OL,8,Femotionally draining all the time. It
OL,9,Fis awful."
OL,11,FHer mother, Mrs Donovan, told the
OL,12,Fcourt how she wondered what Atticus
OL,13,Fwould look like now and what toys he
OL,14,Fwould like to play with.
OL,16,F"I just want one more day with
OL,17,FAtticus," she said.
OL,19,F"I'm glad I had Atticus that night. He
OL,20,Fwas loved and cuddled and had a lovely
OL,21,Fnight with us.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@JO]xD@AOUyD@IO]{D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1784908087
OL,3,CFather jailed for life after murdering
OL,4,Cnewborn baby by shaking him
OL,6,F"I just hope and pray he never knew
OL,7,Fwhat happened to him."
OL,9,FRepresenting Bartlett, Nigel Power KC
OL,10,Fsaid his client had previously been a
OL,11,F"good and caring parent" to his son.
OL,13,F"This is not a case where there is
OL,14,Fintention to kill or premeditation,"
OL,15,FMr Power said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@VO]sD@AOUsD@XO]uD@AOUvD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1784908087
OL,3,CFather jailed for life after murdering
OL,4,Cnewborn baby by shaking him
OL,6,FDet Sgt Sarah Bowden, of the Major
OL,7,FCrime Investigation Team, said: "Tony
OL,8,FBartlett was alone with Atticus when
OL,9,Fhe suffered these horrendous injuries
OL,10,Fand the medical evidence gathered
OL,11,Fduring the investigation proves he was
OL,12,Fsolely responsible for causing them,
OL,13,Fdespite his claims of innocence.
OL,15,F"This is a devastating case in which a
OL,16,Fvery young baby has lost his life as
OL,17,Fthe direct result of a cruel act by a
OL,18,Fman who was supposed to provide him
OL,19,Fwith the protection and care he needed.
OL,26,@oD@aOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1784908087
OL,3,CFather jailed for life after murdering
OL,4,Cnewborn baby by shaking him
OL,6,F"The loss of Atticus has had a
OL,7,Fprofound effect on all those who loved
OL,8,Fhim. Our thoughts are very much with
OL,9,FAtticus' family who've had to endure a
OL,10,Flengthy and complex police
OL,11,Finvestigation, followed by a trial.
OL,12,FThey've shown great dignity and
OL,13,Fcourage throughout.
OL,15,F"Investigations like this are
OL,16,Fextremely harrowing and I'd like to
OL,17,Fthank all those who provided evidence
OL,18,Fand supported our investigation to
OL,19,Festablish the facts behind Atticus'
OL,20,Ftragic death."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
